{"id":2967,"date":"2012-04-19T20:11:51","date_gmt":"2012-04-19T16:11:51","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=2967"},"modified":"2022-10-25T11:39:08","modified_gmt":"2022-10-25T07:39:08","slug":"jihad-tear-open-heart","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/19\/jihad-tear-open-heart\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Jihad: Did you tear open his heart to see his intention?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Usamah ibn Zayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, sent us on an expedition. In the morning we attacked Al-Huraqat of Juhaynah. I caught hold of a man and he said, \u201cThere is no God but Allah!\u201d I stabbed him anyway. Then, it occurred to me that I should mention that to the Prophet. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Did he say &#8216;there is no God but Allah&#8217; but you killed him?<\/strong>\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, he only said it because he feared the weapon!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Did you tear open his heart to know if he meant it or not?<\/strong>\u201d The Prophet continued repeating it to me until I had wished I had not embraced Islam until that day.<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 96<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih <\/em><\/strong>(authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0628\u064e\u0639\u064e\u062b\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064d \u0641\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0628\u064e\